      How do I apply for a Echs card online?
      (i) Visit ECHS website http://www.echs.gov.in then click on the tab Online Smart Card Application Online Application. (ii) Enter your name, service number along with valid mobile number and e-mail ID (for receiving One Time Password) and new password then click on tab Register.

      How do I check my Echs card status?
      There is also an app called "ECHS Beneficiaries App" in Play Store for Android users. Install this app and when you open it click on "Card Status" and give your registered phone number. It will show the status of your card instantly. Thank you.10 Oct 2018

      How do I use my Echs card?
      On subscribing to ECHS, (after retirement) you receive a Smart Card for yourself and your dependents. Report to the nearest ECHS with the card, (you and your dependents will have to go in person there for the first time). Register there and then you can use the services of ECHS.
